<% provide(:title, "Home") %>
<div class="container-fluid block block-1">
  <div class="layer">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12 center-lg">
        <h1>SHE | The Web App</h1>
        <h2>Relationship Simplified</h2>
        <%= link_to 'Sign Up', signup_path, class: 'btn-lg' %>
        <%= link_to 'What is SHE?', "#", id: 'what' %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container-fluid block block-2">
  <div class="row row-block">
    <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-2">
      <%= image_tag("SheLogo1.png") %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h1>What is SHE?</h1>
      <p>
        SHE is a cross platform fake girlfriend web application. SHE was
        created so that you can convince your friends and family that you have
        a girlfriend. Need to impress your family? SHE has you covered. Need to
        impress your friends? SHE can do that. Need to impress your coworkers?
        SHE is the answer.
      </p>
      <%= link_to 'How does SHE work?', "#", id: 'how' %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container-fluid block block-3">
  <div class="row row-block">
    <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-2">
      <h1>How Does it Work?</h1>
      <p>
        She works with a number of different applications in order to
        convince other people that you have a girlfriend. SHE uses Twitter
        to direct message you. SHE can like your posts on Facebook. And SHE
        can send you text messages. All of these features can be used to prove
        to others that you have a girlfriend.
      </p>
      <%= link_to 'How to sign up?', "#", id: 'signup' %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <%= image_tag("Apps.png") %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container-fluid block block-4">
  <div class="row row-block">
    <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-2">
      <%= image_tag("FakeConvo3.png") %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h1>How Do I Sign Up?</h1>
      <p>
        Go to the top of this page and click on the sign up link. Fill out the
        form, and we'll take it from here. Soon, your life will blossom with new
        opportunities, as we populate your Twitter and Facebook with fabricated
        female interaction. Before long, everyone will be totally stoked about you
        and your totally fake girlfriend.
      </p>
      <%= link_to "#" do %>
          <%= image_tag("uparrow.png", size: "50x50", class: 'back-to-top') %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
